Cancato
Chile


Ingredients

Salmon Fillet
Gruyere
Longaniza/Chorizo
Tomatoes
Onion
Garlic
Lemon
Oregano
Dry White Wine


Show Oregano
Show Fish
Slice Gruyere
Dice 200g Chorizo (slices are more traditional)
Juice 1Tbsp Lemon
Slice 3 Cloves Garlic
Julienne 1 Onion
Slice 1 Tomato

Marinate Fish with
	Lemon Juice
	Garlic
	Salt
	Pepper
For 1hr in Fridge
Preheat oven to 180C/375F
Layer onion slices in baking dish
Place Salmon fillets on top
Layer 
	cheese
	Tomatoes
	Chorizo
	Oregano
	S&P
Bake 20min
Deglaze with white wine
Broil for 5min
Serve